Last nights @slayerbandofficial show was out of control. Let me just say that if these guys didn’t exist I don’t think there would of ever been @systemofadown . They took us out on our first American and European tours in 98. They taught us the way of the road. I personally look at them as our metal godparents. It’s sad to know that this might be the last time I see them live. Having said that. Here’s a lil bit of one of the greatest parts ever written by any band. SOUND UP!! 🤘🏼🤘🏼🤘🏼#rainingblood #reigninblood #slayer #theforum #primus #ministry #philanselmoandtheillegals #losangeles. thank you @garyholt_official 🤘🏼🤘🏼
